  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932070/extras/0593284fc21ba5b2f29918212a222544.avif?t=1769645575\" width=616 height=192 /></span><br><br><strong>FEARFUL INJECTION</strong><br><br>In this game you play as Paula, a young nurse working in a hospital. You take over a night shift for one of your colleagues but soon discover that more sinister things are going on. Will you survive the night? Talk to ghosts, banish evil spirits and uncover Paula's past through phone calls, lore and more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932070/extras/8e8c31c898eef2fcbc716caf33771d9f.avif?t=1769645575\" width=616 height=192 /></span><br><br><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>discover the hospital wing and its secrets<br></li><li>find out more about Paula's past and struggles<br></li><li>find anomalies in 8 different rooms<br></li><li>talk to 10 ghosts, each with their own lore<br></li><li>unlock both endings through actions during your playthrough</li></ul><br><strong>LEAVE A REVIEW</strong><br><br>If you enjoy the game or have criticism, please leave a review!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932070/extras/0593284fc21ba5b2f29918212a222544.avif?t=1769645575\" width=616 height=192 /></span><br><br><strong>FEARFUL INJECTION</strong><br><br>In this game you play as Paula, a young nurse working in a hospital. You take over a night shift for one of your colleagues but soon discover that more sinister things are going on. Will you survive the night? Talk to ghosts, banish evil spirits and uncover Paula's past through phone calls, lore and more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932070/extras/8e8c31c898eef2fcbc716caf33771d9f.avif?t=1769645575\" width=616 height=192 /></span><br><br><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>discover the hospital wing and its secrets<br></li><li>find out more about Paula's past and struggles<br></li><li>find anomalies in 8 different rooms<br></li><li>talk to 10 ghosts, each with their own lore<br></li><li>unlock both endings through actions during your playthrough</li></ul><br><strong>LEAVE A REVIEW</strong><br><br>If you enjoy the game or have criticism, please leave a review!",
